'''Tacawit''' nɣ '''Tawrasyant''' tga tutlayt nna s sawaln [[Icawiyn]] ɣ tsga n [[Awras]] ɣ tmazirt n [[Dzayr]]. Tkka-d Tacawit tawja n [[tutlayin timaziɣin]].

Lwilayat nna ɣ tettyusawal tutlayt-ad gan-tnt: Tabatnt, Xnclt, Suq Ahras, Um Lbwaqi, Tbssa, Qsnṭina, tiɣawinin ɣ unẓul n Sṭif d umur n ugafa n tmaẓlayt (tawilayt) n Tbskrt.

